msgid "Breath lyrics"
msgstr "呼吸音歌词"

msgid "Special lyrics that will be recognized as breath notes only when immediately followed by a regular note, each separated by a space"
msgstr "仅在之后紧跟一个普通音符时才会被识别为呼吸音符的特殊歌词，歌词之间用空格隔开。"

msgid "Silence lyrics"
msgstr "休止符歌词"

msgid "Special lyrics that will be ignored, each separated by a space"
msgstr "将被忽略的特殊歌词，歌词之间用空格隔开"

msgid "The way to handle english multisyllabic words"
msgstr "处理英文多音节单词的方式"

msgid "Compatibility with ARPAsing-series Phonemizer"
msgstr "与 ARPAsing系列音素器的兼容性"

